Dialogue: 1,0:08:23.85,0:08:28.94,辉中,,0,0,0,,Whether you want to document the future of spaceflight or show off your unique skill,
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.04,0:08:33.26,辉中,,0,0,0,,check out this class called 'YouTube Success' by Marques Brownlee.
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:37.99,辉中,,0,0,0,,Whether you know a lot about the YouTube industry or are just starting out,
